	<pb facs="liv_012056_0051" n="0051"/>
<lb/><p><fw rend="small"><add place="marginleft">25</add></fw>
<lb/>to steal some of the loads others remained
<lb/>quiet, the <orgName>Zanzibaris</orgName> at first <unclear cert="medium">grasped</unclear>
<lb/>their guns and wanted to fight the
<lb/><term type="ethnic-group">Manyema</term> but <persName>Bonny</persName> interfered <!-- Not sure if this is Bonny or another name?? HB -->
<lb/>and quiet was returned -</p>
<lb/><p><persName><unclear cert="medium">Tanga</unclear></persName> ran away to the <geogName type="waterfall">Falls</geogName> - <!-- geog: Stanley or Victoria Falls(?) -->
<lb/>and <unclear>gave</unclear> himself up to <persName>Tippu Tib</persName>
<lb/>In the Evening of <persName>Barttelot</persName>'s death
<lb/>both <orgName>Zanzibaris</orgName> &amp; <term type="ethnic-group">Londanese</term> danced
<lb/>and sang &amp; burned down the wooden
<lb/>triangle in which they had so
<lb/>often been <choice><abbr>lash'd</abbr><expan>lashed</expan></choice> &amp; flogged; <unclear cert="medium">and</unclear>
<lb/>played the drum where the
<lb/>whipping place once stood -</p>

	<pb facs="liv_012056_0052" n="0052"/>
<lb/><!-- blank page HB -->

	<pb facs="liv_012056_0053" n="0053"/>
<lb/><fw rend="small"><add place="marginleft">26</add></fw>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">. <persName>Jamieson</persName> learning of the <roleName>Major</roleName>'s death
<lb/>repaired to <persName>Tippu Tib</persName> &amp; demanded that
<lb/><persName>Tanga</persName> should be <unclear cert="low">encanted</unclear> which was <!-- unclear should have "super-low" as an option...I have no idea what that word is! HB -->
<lb/>duly carried our - The <orgName>Arabs</orgName> said
<lb/>they were very sorry but <persName>Jamieson</persName>
<lb/>remarked that "<persName><roleName>Major</roleName> Barttelot</persName>
<lb/>had killed himself"- one old <orgName>Arab</orgName>
<lb/><persName>Talim Masoodi</persName> stated that according
<lb/>to their own custom <persName>Tanga</persName> ought
<lb/>not to die - "a man who <choice><sic>illtreats</sic><corr>ill-treats</corr></choice>
<lb/>another man's wife is liable to
<lb/>death by their woman's husband
<lb/>who however is not punishd
<lb/>the indignity offered to the woman
<lb/>being sufficient reason to acquit him

	<pb facs="liv_012056_0054" n="0054"/>
<lb/><!-- blank page HB -->

	<pb facs="liv_012056_0055" n="0055"/>
<lb/><fw rend="small"><add place="marginleft">27</add></fw>
<lb/>this is the spirit of the <orgName>Arab</orgName> and
<lb/><term type="nationality">Swahili</term> law, but the major being <!-- Not sure if the nationality tag is the right one here? HB -->
<lb/>a <orgName>whiteman</orgName> the law became <w>in<seg type="hyphen">-</seg>
<lb break="no"/>applicable</w> -</p>
<lb/><p><space extent="2" unit="chars"/>After the <roleName>Major</roleName>'s death the
<lb/>whole <orgName>Expedition</orgName> became disorganized
<lb/>&amp; the <term type="ethnic-group">Manyema</term>'s deserted on all sides
<lb/>from <placeName>Banalya</placeName>, and when <persName>Stanley</persName>
<lb/>returned he found <persName>Bonny</persName> the
<lb/>sole <orgName>whiteman</orgName> in command
<lb/>&amp; a few wretched <orgName>Zanzibaris</orgName> who
<lb/>were covered with <unclear><term type="ailment">sores</term></unclear> &amp; reduced
<lb/>to mere skeletons by the many
<lb/>months of <unclear cert="low">withcatment</unclear> &amp; hunger; not
<lb/>one of them was able to carry a

	<pb facs="liv_012056_0056" n="0056"/>
<lb/><!-- blank page HB -->

	<pb facs="liv_012056_0057" n="0057"/>
<lb/><fw rend="small"><add place="marginleft">28</add></fw>
<lb/>load.</p>
<lb/><p>. <persName>Ludi <choice><sic>Barttelots</sic><corr>Barttelot's</corr></choice></persName> little boy was
<lb/>suffering from a <term type="ailment">festering wound</term> on
<lb/>the leg which he had received from
<lb/>a kick by the <roleName>Major</roleName> - He was going
<lb/>to wash the <roleName>Major</roleName>'s feet one day
<lb/>and had taken off one sock and
<lb/>boot but the water proved too
<lb/>cold and <persName>Barttelot</persName> <del type="strikethrough">which</del> resented
<lb/>this by kicking <persName>Ludi</persName> with his heavy
<lb/>boot cutting the boy's shin to the
<lb/>bone, &amp; making a wound which
<lb/>the <choice><sic>boys</sic><corr>boy's</corr></choice> impoverished condition son
<lb/><unclear>condensed</unclear> in <term type="ailment">festering sore</term> from
<lb/>which the <del type="cancelled">boy</del> eventually died.</p>

	<pb facs="liv_012056_0058" n="0058"/>
<lb/><!-- blank page HB -->

	<pb facs="liv_012056_0059" n="0059"/>
<lb/><fw rend="small"><add place="marginleft">25</add></fw>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">. The <orgName>Zanzibaris</orgName> &amp; <orgName>Arabs</orgName> said that
<lb/>had there been a man in command
<lb/>at <placeName>Yambuya</placeName> who had <unclear cert="low">swerared</unclear>
<lb/>due tact in dealing with the <orgName>Arabs</orgName>
<lb/>and had that man been honest <space extent="2" unit="chars"/>of
<lb/>purpose and capable of proving
<lb/>that he was so - men to carry
<lb/>loads would have been forthcoming
<lb/>From <persName>Tippu Tib</persName> and the rear
<lb/>column would have moved
<lb/>soon after <persName>Stanley</persName> - But the <orgName>Arabs</orgName>
<lb/>say that the actions of <persName>Jamieson</persName>
<lb/>&amp; <persName>Barttelot</persName> destroyed all <choice><sic>confidance</sic><corr>confidence</corr></choice>
<lb/><persName>Jamieson</persName> offered money of his own
<lb/>if <persName>Tippu Tib</persName> would make an effort

	<pb facs="liv_012056_0060" n="0060"/>
<lb/><!-- blank page HB -->

	<pb facs="liv_012056_0061" n="0061"/>
<lb/><fw rend="small"><add place="marginleft">30</add></fw>
<lb/>to supply the men, but he said in
<lb/>that case he would have the <unclear cert="medium">sole</unclear>
<lb/>direction of the enterprise &amp; command
<lb/>the Rear Column -</p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><persName>Barttelot</persName> said that <persName>Stanley</persName> was
<lb/>dead but he wanted to reach <unclear cert="low">Smin</unclear>
<lb/>but would take a shorter road
<lb/>to <unclear><placeName>Wadelai</placeName></unclear> than the path made
<lb/>by <persName>Stanley</persName> -</p>
<lb/><p>. <persName><choice><sic>Barttelots</sic><corr>Barttelot's</corr></choice></persName>, well known harshness
<lb/>&amp; inability to deal with <orgName>blacks</orgName>, all
<lb/>prevented the recruitment of men
<lb/>&amp; the fulfillment of <persName>Tippu Tib</persName>'s
<lb/>promise to <persName>Stanley</persName>.</p>


	<pb facs="liv_012056_0062" n="0062"/>
<lb/><!-- blank page HB -->

	<pb facs="liv_012056_0063" n="0063"/>
<lb/><p><fw rend="small"><add place="marginleft"><hi rend="underline">31</hi></add></fw>
<lb/><unclear cert="low">Trump</unclear> did all he could to <!-- I tried to see any other word but this one, and I can't...help, Ann! HB -->
<lb/>alleviate the sufferings of the <orgName>Zanzabaris</orgName>
<lb/>&amp; protested against <persName><choice><sic>Barttelots</sic><corr>Barttelot's</corr></choice></persName> inhuman
<lb/>conduct - but he was confined to
<lb/>his bed by <term type="ailment">severe sickness</term> and
<lb/><persName>Barttleot</persName> ordered that none of the
<lb/><orgName>Zanzibaris</orgName> were to visit his hut -</p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">. <persName>Bonny</persName> also made a protest &amp;
<lb/>in one <choice><sic>occassion</sic><corr>occasion</corr></choice> the <roleName>Major</roleName> ordered
<lb/>the <term type="ethnic-group">Londanese</term> to arrest <persName>Bonny</persName>
<lb/>For insubordination <unclear cert="medium">he</unclear> having
<lb/>presented <persName>Barttelot</persName> by force
<lb/>from striking someone; But
<lb/>the <term type="ethnic-group">Londanese</term> did not obey <unclear cert="medium">as</unclear> <persName>Bonny</persName>
<lb/>threatened to defend themselves -</p>

	<pb facs="liv_012056_0064" n="0064"/>
<lb/><!-- blank page HB -->

			</div>
            <div rend="black">

	<pb facs="liv_012056_0065" n="0065"/>
<lb/><fw rend="small"><add place="marginleft"><hi rend="underline">32</hi></add></fw>
<lb/><p>The above narration is supplied
<lb/>by <persName>Saleh Bin Osman</persName>, <persName>Mr Stanley</persName>'s
<lb/><orgName><orgName>Zanzibari</orgName> <term type="occupation">servant</term></orgName>, he tells his story
<lb/><add place="marginleft">of</add> what he learned, concerning these
<lb/>events, from <orgName>Zanzibaris</orgName>, <orgName>Arabs</orgName>
<lb/><term type="ethnic-group">Manyemas</term>, &amp; <term type="ethnic-group">Londanese</term> who
<lb/>witnessed the different events <unclear>enumerated</unclear></p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">I have carefully translated from <persName><unclear cert="low">Kin Swaheli</unclear>
<lb/>Saleh</persName>'s words &amp; do hereby solemnly
<lb/>declare that I have truthfully
<lb/>worded all he said</p>
<lb/><p><space extent="3" unit="words"/><date when="1890-11-12"><choice><abbr>Nov</abbr><expan>November</expan></choice> 12. <choice><abbr>90</abbr><expan>1890</expan></choice>.</date></p>
<lb/><p><space extent="2" unit="words"/><settlement type="city">New York</settlement></p>
<lb/><p><space extent="3" unit="words"/><persName>E. J Glave</persName>.</p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><hi rend="underline">Witnesses</hi></p>
<lb/><p><persName>John B. Ritche</persName>
<lb/><persName>J B Pond</persName></p>

	<pb facs="liv_012056_0066" n="0066"/>
